{"tid":1799561,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[集思廣益]一人一個和你shop之後解鎖嘅武器","createTime":"2019-12-27T05:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T06:37:28.000Z","uid":89974,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e57118642bd7d2abbbc7aa5e4db0dead54ed2342","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"之前一直俾人遠距離火力轟炸，好多武器(如漆彈)都用唔著<br />\n而家和你shop除咗仲係好難打得贏嘅防暴，便衣先係主力，而便衣係無乜防具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我地變相都無得帶文具，但係對面都無得好似以前咁實彈/TG放題(或者話實彈/TG放題都係我地贏，攬炒)<br />\n<br />\n大家係時候諗下有咩易帶，帶咗又唔會identify到你身份嘅武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你唔進攻用，你都至少有半分鐘至一分鐘嘅機會救到手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1.漆彈</strong></span><br />\n易帶效果好，但俾人逗有機會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2.汽水+萬樂珠</span></strong><br />\n易帶，唔會中伏，一人一支顏射效果極爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觸發後成支丟落便衣人群入面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3.鹽/糖/吉野家七味粉/細粒得嚟入眼會痛到仆街嘅野</strong></span><br />\n除非你商場帶黑超，否則四方八面遠距離投擲，佢地好難防，仲可以消耗吉野家嘅七味粉，雙贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4.熱水</strong></span><br />\n香港商場冷氣咁大，做個良好市民幫佢保吓溫，雖然濕身俾風吹仲凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋地下濕就唔好跑步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有無？"},{"pid":"fb3375d0f99516da5c723f1daf92b9cd3d427d71","tid":1799561,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"鯡魚罐頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28c3fee20fb913605373192e4d6a9844dcac513","tid":1799561,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9L7WaCm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9L7WaCm.jpg&h=d4e9d5b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d6ee9b36e78e4f2ed7d603bd64861c6bd2ee1be","tid":1799561,"uid":71997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"梅香鹹魚"},{"pid":"b77d754a81082316c6d512ebc0d14f7db4249c3f","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8516a81c82763a20572aa17f6e09072b90cfc0a","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3375d0f99516da5c723f1daf92b9cd3d427d71","tid":1799561,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"鯡魚罐頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"帶出街俾人check好難兜喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350b346e1a3652d53a9d169c0707920fba5070a8","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48012fc431a93c64c7bcaa034db6fb25ca89d68","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9220be42fd5f26bde3ffd1d528fdf3c81d0ff00f","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963daeaa703126d99d69becc00604fe13dea84ef","tid":1799561,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/